<pb facs="1079215" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Illustrissimo atque Celeberrimo <choice><abbr>Jo:</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/>Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Duodecim jam excurrunt dies ex quo fasciculum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimarum Tuar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/><rs key="biblio_JAFFCHKU" type="biblio">de Motu Musculorum</rs>, ac <rs key="biblio_W6BHQDM2" type="biblio">de Effervescentia, et Fermentatione</rs> Dissertation<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">de Separatione Fluidorum in Corpore Animali</rs> Dissertationi conjunc<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tarum per <rs key="place_GEO-3173435" type="place">Mediolanum</rs> ad Te transmisi. Nunc quoniam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam ori<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur ad Te scribendi occasio, me Tibi esse devinctissimum propter omnia
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">Dissertationem</rs> meam apprime facientia<note type="editorial">sic.</note> mecum communicasti
         <lb/>rursus confiteor. Scribendi autem occasio h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c est. Ante quindecim dies
         <lb/>verba faciens de rebus mathematicis cum Comite Jacobo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccato</rs>, et ab hoc sci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>scitatus num perspexerit (quotidie enim jactare solet se plurima in <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newt<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>oni</rs> <rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio">libris</rs><note type="editorial">werktag: newtonbhbd auf BEOL und schon für den Platzhalter eingesetzt: Newton, Princ. Math., 1713. <!-- ToDo: korrekt mit neuer biblio-ID verlinken --></note> falsa invenisse, <hi rend="u">uti et in quibusdam Tuis inventis ad oscillatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes pendulorum in diversis Fluidis pertinentibus</hi> etc<supplied>.</supplied>) falsitatem <choice><abbr>Corol.</abbr><expan>Corollarii</expan></choice> 2<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>
         <lb/><choice><abbr>proposit.</abbr><expan>propositionis</expan></choice> XXXVI<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio">Operis</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoniani</rs>, respondit se jam pridem
         <lb/>cognovisse ejusmodi <choice><abbr>corollar.</abbr><expan>corollarium</expan></choice> falsum esse, postea alia die error<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <choice><sic>corexisse</sic><corr>correxis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>se</corr></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newton<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> in editione <rs key="place_GEO-2759794" type="place">Amstelodamensi</rs><!-- ToDo: Bibliotag: Newton, Principia, Ausgabe Amstaelodami (Amsterdam) 1714. --> pronunciavit: at quum e<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> os<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tendiss<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ead<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> die ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newton<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> <rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio">Corollari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> non mutasse in eadem
         <lb/>illa ultima <rs key="place_GEO-2759794" type="place">Amstelodami</rs> editione acquievit. Dom<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> reversus post oc<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>to dies ad me scripsit<note type="editorial">Brief nachweisen.</note>, se considerasse attentissime <rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio">Corollari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Vermutlich ebenfalls die Principia Newtons, aber welche Ausgabe ist gemeint?</note>, de quo loquor,
         <lb/>et illud ver<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> invenisse. Conatus autem est veritat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ejusmodi <rs key="biblio_6CP8LL78" type="biblio">"Corollarii</rs><note type="editorial">Vermutlich ebenfalls die Principia Newtons, aber welche Ausgabe ist gemeint?</note>
<lb/>sequenti ratiocinio demonstrare. "Loquitur (inquit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>) <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtonus</rs>
<lb/>in 2. <choice><abbr>Corollar.</abbr><expan>Corollario</expan></choice> de aqua, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> dato tempore ex vase egreditur, nimirum
         <lb/>de quantitate aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egreditur eo tempore, quo ipsa aqua motu accele<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rato descenderet per altitudinem <formula>2IG</formula>, vel <formula>2CK</formula><supplied>"</supplied>. Id vero deducere ni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>titur <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs> ex illis <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoni</rs> verbis. <hi rend="u">Nam aqua exiliens quo tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pore hanc columnam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quat, pondere suo ab altitudine <formula>GI</formula> ca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dendo, velocitatem suam, qua exilit acquirere potest.</hi><note hand="pers_DE-588-102552517"><choice><abbr>Vid.</abbr><expan>Vide</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>fig.</abbr><expan>figuram</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person"><choice><abbr>Newt.</abbr><expan>Newtoni</expan></choice></rs></note><note resp="SG" type="editorial">Der Verweis bezieht sich auf die Figur auf p. 308 von der 2. Auflage von Newtons Principia. <!-- (https://www.e-rara.ch/zut/content/pageview/338960) --></note> Id eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
         <lb/>deduci putat ex aliis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in tertio <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoni</rs> Corollario continentur, ver<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c sunt. <hi rend="u">Et aqua per foramen egrediens, quo tempore gutta ca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dendo ab <formula>I</formula> describere posset altitudinem <formula>IG</formula>, <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis erit cylindro, cujus ba<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sis est circulus <formula>EF</formula>, et altitudo est <formula>2IG</formula></hi>. Nullam in hac ultima assertione
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoniana</rs> esse difficultat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> hac ratione ostendit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>: Quia
         <lb/>si ponamus <formula>V</formula> velocitat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gutta <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> puncto summo <formula>I</formula> descendendo
         <lb/>per altitudin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <formula>IG</formula> acquireret in ultimo puncto <formula>G</formula>; liquet ex <rs key="pers_DE-588-118537229" type="person">Galilei</rs>
<lb/>demonstratis posse ejusmodi velocitat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentari per <formula>2GI</formula>
<lb/>quia aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gutta velocitate acquisita ex casu per <formula>IG</formula>
<pb facs="1079216" n="2"/>
<lb/>motu uniformi <choice><sic>percurere</sic><corr>percurrere</corr></choice> posset spati<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>2GI</formula>. Quoni<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> aut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> spatia <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bili eod<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> tempore motu uniformi percursa sunt ut velocitates: ec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quis non videt (inquit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>) velocitat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <formula>V</formula> exprimi posse per <formula>2GI</formula>.
         <lb/>Quod si admittamus (rursus inquit) quia quantitas aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> dato
         <lb/>tempore per foramen vasis egrediens est ut orificium forami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis duct<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in velocitat<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, necessario sequitur <formula>V</formula> duc<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>t<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in orificium foraminis <formula>EF</formula>, sive <formula>2GI\times EF</formula> esse quantita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egress<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per foramen <formula>EF</formula> quo tempore aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gutta
         <lb/>ex summo puncto <formula>I</formula> cadendo motu accelerato spatium
         <lb/><formula>IG</formula> emensa est. His pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>missis veritatem Corollarii <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoniani</rs>
<lb/>demonstrare pergit. Corollari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> (ut nosti) est hujusmodi.
         <lb/><hi rend="u">Et vis, qua totus aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exilientis motus generari potest <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis est pon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deri cylindric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, cujus basis est foramen <formula>EF</formula>, et altitudo <formula>2IG</formula></hi>.</p> <p>Per vim mot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aliquem producent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> nihil aliud intelli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>git <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtonus</rs> (inquit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>) nisi vim quand<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> ad mot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> solli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citantem, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> posito tempore constanti est ut quantitas mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tus, sive ut massa ducta in velocitatem, et posita etiam velo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citate constanti vis erit ut massa. In <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoni</rs> casu (inquit
               <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs>) tempus ponitur <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quale ei, quod insumeret aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gutta 
               <lb/>cadens ex puncto <formula>I</formula> per altitudinem <formula>IG</formula>, velocitas, qua aqua
               <lb/>exilit ex foramine <formula>EF</formula> etiam ponitur semper eadem; igitur vis
               <lb/>motum aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> generans <hi rend="u"><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis est moli aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> eodem illo tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pore exit ex foramine <formula>EF</formula>. Sed moles aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> dato illo tempore egress<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis cylindro cujus basis <formula>EF</formula>, altitudo ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro <formula>2GI</formula> (uti modo demonstrat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> est) quare etiam vis
               <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tot<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exilientis <choice><sic>motus</sic><corr>motum</corr></choice> generat <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis cylindro
